name: WARHOL EMERGES
description:
Digital sculpture > digitally painted animation of Andy Warhol emerging from the cosmic microwave background.

And then returning, ad nauseam.

Created to celebrate the 8th issue of the @inwarhol zine, In the Tickle of Warhol’s Fruit, inspired by The Plastic Exploding Inevitable. Created by Wily Guys and Maia Mellier.
